<pattern>WHAT IS TALF</pattern>
<template>
TALF (The Asian Lenses Forum) is a first of a kind initiative taken by NIIT University to sensitize the young generation to their heritage. 
The forum held its 3rd Annual Conference on 23rd September 2016 at Russian Centre for Science and Culture, Delhi.
