<pattern>TELL ME ABOUT THE DINING FACILITIES IN NU</pattern>
<template>The three spacious and airy dining halls are where students and faculty have their food together. 
Breakfast, lunch, a high tea and dinner are served here. 
Food served is primarily vegetarian, with eggs being served on some days.
The menu is decided by the Mess Committee comprising mainly of students and a few faculty members. 
Parents and invited guests too have their meals here.</template>
